snippet.title: PyxelKnight V1.0.5
snippet.description:
Pyxel Knight V1.0.5 is live! Featuring a new Iguana monster and a challenging moving level stage. Things should get pretty exciting.
Also the ability to set your own controls which has been requested several times is now available.

Get it now at http://www.pyxelknight.com
Vote for Pyxel Knight on Steam https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=883295772
